gw.api.policy.refresh.relink

Class RelinkBeanImpl<T extends KeyableBean>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.policy.refresh.relink.RelinkBeanImpl<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RelinkBean<T>

    public class RelinkBeanImpl<T extends KeyableBean>
extends java.lang.Object
implements RelinkBean<T>
    Represents a bean in the existing Claim/Policy that needs to be relinked when the existing Policy is replaced. The RelinkBean may be either the "source" (in the existing policy) or the "target" (in the non-policy Claim) for the link.
    Author:
    bspies
